              |                                 
              .text-right
                a(href='#')
                  | View Details 
                  i.fa.fa-arrow-circle-right
        |                     
        .col-lg-6
          .panel.panel-primary
            .panel-heading
              h3.panel-title
                i.fa.fa-long-arrow-right
                |  Bar Graph with Tooltips
            |                             
            .panel-body
              .flot-chart
                #flot-bar-chart.flot-chart-content
              |                                 
              .text-right
                a(href='#')
                  | View Details 
                  i.fa.fa-arrow-circle-right
      // /.row
      // Morris Charts
      .row
        .col-lg-12
          h2.page-header Morris Charts
          |                         
          p.lead
            | Morris.js is a very simple API for drawing line, bar, area and donut charts. For full usage instructions and documentation for Morris.js charts, visit 
            a(href='http://www.oesmith.co.uk/morris.public/js/') http://www.oesmith.co.uk/morris.public/js/
            | .
      // /.row
      .row
        .col-lg-12
          .panel.panel-green
            .panel-heading
              h3.panel-title
                i.fa.fa-bar-chart-o
                |  Area Line Graph Example with Tooltips
            |                             
            .panel-body
              #morris-area-chart
      // /.row
      .row
        .col-lg-4
          .panel.panel-yellow
            .panel-heading
